{"tid":1498226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連日市民圍堵車站促交代警暴 港鐵最快今晚申臨時禁制令","createTime":"2019-08-23T10:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:18:17.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f193da0af5d85a27fe782d58af0c412b1c188e4b","tid":1498226,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190823/large/1566554900_8feb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190823%2Flarge%2F1566554900_8feb.jpg&h=702df3f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外界有消息指港鐵正考慮仿效機管局的做法，向法庭申請禁制令禁止示威活動，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆證實，因應葵芳站事件，港鐵正進行處理有關禁制令事宜。但陳帆稱由於禁制令的申請仍在處理，故不作評論，指相信港鐵會向市民交代。據知，港鐵最快今晚申請臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆回應記者提問指，港鐵正在處理。他稱港鐵禁制令因為處理當中，在此不便評論，相信港鐵公司會適時向社會和傳媒公佈。陳帆指，近日有不少港鐵車站遭破壞，站內造成嚴重破壞，市民和員工遭受「人身安全威脅」，正處理禁制令工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190823/59965994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F59965994&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAoD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=c9732760\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F59965994&h=b5e6fa77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190823/59965994</a>"}]}